  "response": "New Delhi has several popular coffee shops known for great coffee. Some top-rated options include:\n\n1. Blue Tokai Coffee Roasters\n- Known for high-quality, freshly roasted coffee\n- Multiple locations in Delhi\n- Artisanal coffee and great brewing techniques\n\n2. The Coffee Bond\n- Specialty coffee shop\n- Great ambiance and variety of coffee preparations\n\n3. Perch Wine & Coffee Bar\n- Offers excellent coffee and a sophisticated environment\n- Known for their expertly crafted beverages\n\n4. Kaffa Espresso Bar\n- Popular for authentic espresso and coffee drinks\n- Multiple branches in the city\n\n5. Social Offline\n- Trendy cafe with good coffee and interesting atmosphere\n- Mix of cafe and co-working space\n\n6. Starbucks\n- Multiple locations\n- Consistent quality and variety of coffee options\n\nThe \"best\" coffee can be subjective, so I recommend trying a few places to find your personal favorite. Each cafe has its unique style and brewing methods.",
